data.description: Welcome home at Fortune Place at Johnson Farms! This 4-bedroom, 3-bath gem sits on a corner lot, offering both comfort & convenience.  Step inside to discover an inviting open living area with LVP wood floors and trey ceilings. The natural gas fireplace adds warmth and charm, while the built-in shelving provides a perfect spot for your cherished books and decor. From here, step into a sunroom featuring LVT flooring and a mini-split HVAC system. Imagine sipping your morning coffee here, basking in the sunlight that floods through and in the evening enjoy the patio w/a gas hookup for your grilling adventures! The heart of this home is the spacious kitchen. With its convenient island, natural gas stove, and a point-of-use water heater under the sink, you'll enjoy instant hot water for your culinary endeavors. The upgraded cabinetry and pantry provide ample storage space. The primary bedroom is a true retreat. It boasts 2 walk-in closets and an ensuite bath with ceramic flooring. The oversized walk-in shower features 2 heads and another tankless water heater for ultimate comfort. The other 2 baths are well appointed w/spacious vanities & quality flooring. A 3-zoned heat pump keeps your energy bills in check while maintaining a comfortable climate. The walk-in, floored attic is perfect for storage. Crown molding and baseboards add a touch of sophistication. The laundry room has ample amount of space and is conveniently located next to the 2.5-car garage. Other bonuses include a generator transfer switch, a full gutter system, and yard irrigation. Fortune Place is a quiet neighborhood, complete with a beautiful clubhouse and community pool. Conveniently situated near Carolina and Wrightsville beaches, downtown attractions, shopping and dining, this home invites you to explore the best of coastal living. Don't wait! Make your plans to visit today and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of.
